<h2>The Lisbon Challenge and the Explorers Festival</h2>

<p>
    Alongside with the <em>João Cabral</em> and <em>Hugo Campos</em>, we hard balled into the TOP 25 (from 75 international startups) at the 2013 edition of <em>The Lisbon Challenge</em>, winning a pitch at the Explorers Festival and a final 12th place in the competition.
</p>
<p>
    In the end, even though we had a good track record with over 6000 users on the platform in only three months, like most startups, we failed to secure an investment that could make the full vision come true.
</p>

