<h2>Spinning Off</h2>

<p>
    Using the experience and contacts acquired during our work at <em>WannaPlayer</em>, we spawned two pitches for new television shows where I was responsible for branding and art directing motion graphics.
</p>
<p>
    The <em>Next Big Player</em> focused on interviews with young and upcoming talent and <em>Secret Scout</em>, which was a match prognosis show, aired for a considerable amount of episodes on the cable channel <em>A Bola TV</em>.
</p>

